nodes.text: A Jedi Master served the Galactic Republic and trained the Human Voren Renstaal as a Jedi.

The master trained the Human Voren Renstaal to become a Jedi, on the planet Ossus. Following the outbreak of the Mandalorian Wars, the master fought alongside Renstaal during the early stages of the conflict. However, the master was killed during the First Battle of Onderon in 3963 BBY.
